ction between different energy centroid\nlines of 6.4 keV vs. 6.7 KeV (or 6.7 keV vs. Cobalt 7.2 keV) is possible up to\nz~0.6, 1.2, and 2 (z~ 1, 5, 7.5), with Swift,Chandra, and XMM respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2004 23:36:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2004 17:31:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2005 14:32:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
