 by relatively short timescales, recurrent outbursts,\nmodest increase in bolometric luminosity and accretion rate, and an\nevolutionary state earlier than that of typical EXors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Aug 2004 08:44:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2007 09:15:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
